,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,NULL,'Key One Realty LLC',NULL),('IT Help Desk','Egypt','Cairo','','Perform troubleshooting using different diagnostic techniques Troubleshoot, diagnose, and resolve technical hardware and/or software issues Response to receive and record user issues and create tickets. Analyze issues and report to his direct manager for any recurring problems. Maintain and troubleshooting user\'s computer, printers, and devices.','Hands on experience with diagnosing and resolving basic technical issues. Good problem-solving, analytical, and team-working skills Excellent communication and interpersonal skills Ability to work in team. BA in IT, Computer Science or similar relevant field Arabic language + English is mandatory.  ','2023-10-31',0,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Entry Level (Junior Level / Fresh Grad)','Bachelor\'s Degree','Kgroup','M'),('IT Operations Manager','Egypt','Cairo','','Maintain IT infrastructure, including operating systems, security tools, applications, servers, email systems, laptops, desktops, software, and hardware. Handle business-critical IT tasks and lead systems administration team. Track and maintain hardware and software inventory. Develops, communicates, and controls the IT policies and procedures ensuring employees conformance to the approved regulations. Manages and supervises the daily processing, development, and maintenance of IT operations. Testing, troubleshooting, and modifying information systems so that they operate effectively. Evaluating technology risks in order to develop a network disaster recovery plan and backup procedures. Oversees the planning, management, and upgrading of the company’s VOIP system. Oversees the management of the help desk activities and apply KPI’s on helpdesk team. Remaining up to date with advances in technology and industry best practices.','Bachelor\'s degree in engineering, computer science, information technology, or any related field (or equivalent experience). Minimum 12 years’ experience. Excellent verbal and written communication skills in English and Arabic. Ability to communicate effectively both written and verbal Skills required: Strong technical knowledge of IT systems and infrastructure. Solid understanding of IT security principles and best practices. Excellent leadership, communication, and problem-solving skills Ability to prioritize tasks, manage multiple projects, and meet deadlines. Strong analytical and decision-making abilities. Experience in Microsoft 365 environment and experience with migration process. Experience with VOIP systems. Experience with SAP Basis is preferred.','2023-10-30',22,14,12,15,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Manager ','Bachelor\'s Degree','Kgroup','M'),('Senior System and Network Administrator','Egypt','Cairo','','Managing and configuring network devices like firewalls, routers, switches. Ensure maximum stability of IT facility infrastructure components by performing system maintenance tasks &system monitoring Monitor network to ensure network availability to all system users and perform necessary maintenance to support network availability. Configure and manage VPN connection between sites. Managing and configuring Windows servers DC1/DC2/Home folder and SQL DB server. Managing and configuring user permission according to Company IT policies. Schedule Databases, exchange and Domain Controller Backups.','Experience in configuring and managing HP Aruba switches and Sonicwall firewall. Work experience support company with multiple sites Prefer experience in G-Suite administration. Ability to work under stress. Ability to work in team. Ability to communicate effectively, both written and verbal Bachelor degree in computer science / Engineering. Arabic language + English is mandatory.','2023-10-31',0,0,10,12,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Manager ','Bachelor\'s Degree','Kgroup','M'),('Full Stack Developer','Egypt','Giza','','Purpose: We are looking for a highly skilled computer programmer who is comfortable with both front and back end programming. Full stack developers are responsible for developing and designing front end web architecture, ensuring the responsiveness of applications, and working alongside graphic designers for web design features, among other duties. Job Responsibilities: Responsible on coding, testing and implementing software enhancements. Developing frontend website, Mobile and POS application architecture. Designing user interactions on web page, Mobile and POS application. Developing backend website, Mobile and POS applications. Creating servers and databases for functionality. Ensuring cross-platform optimization for mobile phones or any other digital device i.e. POS. Ensuring responsiveness of applications. Working alongside graphic designers for UX/UI design features. Seeing through a project from conception to finished product. Designing and developing APIs. Meeting both technical and consumer needs. Staying abreast of developments in web applications and programming languages.','BSc degree in Computer Science or relevant field Proven work experience1 – 3 Years ANDROID, JAVA, SPRING, C++, KOTLIN & entry level for any database tool: ORACLE or MS SQL Server In-depth understanding of the entire web development process (design, development and deployment)JAVA, SPRING, C++, KOTLIN & entry level for any database tool: ORACLE or MS SQL Server Excellent analytical and time management skills Teamwork skills with a problem-solving attitude','2023-10-01',30,0,1,3,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Experienced (Non-Manager)',NULL,'Khales',NULL),('Senior Solution Architecture Engineer','Egypt','Cairo','','Experience in gathering, eliciting validating, verifying, and documenting business solutions and integration requirements. Experience in writing software specifications. Have the capabilities to design valuable solutions considering the organization capabilities, evaluate them, in addition to build knowledge and improve process. Experience in technically leading development and implementation teams. As 