mpetencies Collaboration Accountability Resilience Quality Leadership Application Server Platforms  L3Application Sizing L3Hardware Management L3Account Access Management L3Creates Strategy - Developing Drives Performance - Developing Develops Future Leaders - Developing Security and Monitoring L3Education','Skills\nAnalyzes existing programs or formulates logic for new systems, devises logic procedures, prepares flowcharting, performs coding and tests/debugs programs. Develops conversion and system implementation plans. Prepares and obtains approval of system and programming documentation. Recommends changes in development, maintenance and system standards.','2023-10-12',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,'Manager ',NULL,'Power International Holding',NULL),('.Net React Full-stack Developer','Egypt','Cairo','','Key Responsibilities:  Develop and maintain web applications using C# or VB. NET and React. Design and implement web services (WCF and Web API) to create a service-oriented architecture. Work with SQL Server, including T-SQL and SSIS, for data management. Utilize XML/XSL for data transformation and integration. Apply object-oriented programming (OOP) principles and design patterns in development. Follow test-driven development (TDD) practices to ensure code quality and reliability. Work with . NET 4.0 onwards and related technologies, including Ajax, Java Script, j Query, CSS. Utilize Visual Studio 2013 for application development. Collaborate with cross-functional teams to enhance and maintain Winforms enterprise applications. Maintain code version control using Subversion. Work with continuous integration tools like Team City. Demonstrate knowledge of build tools and virtualization. Understand and apply UML (Unified Modeling Language) principles when necessary  ','Qualifications:  Bachelor’s degree in computer science, Information Technology, or a related field. Proven experience as a full-stack developer with a strong background in . NET and 