ent Systems. Our goal is to enable localizing 50% of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia’s spending on Combat systems for military naval systems by 2030. Our vision is to be the top leading military naval system company in Saudi Arabia and the region, by developing world-class combat systems and providing high-quality services to our clients through cutting-edge technologies and the best national engineering talents and capabilities. Responsibilities Collaborate with stakeholders to gather, define and analyze system requirements. Write clean, maintainable, and efficient Requirements & Specifications. (system and software requirements)  Stay up-to-date with emerging trends and technologies in the software development industry. Develop Test Procedures. Develop system engineering plans. Conduct system/software testing. System architecture definition. Utilize requirement traceability tools to ensure project development aligns with initial requirements and objectives. Document system requirements, design specifications, and other necessary project artifacts. Define interfaces specifications with external equipment. Supporting the integration and deployment of software systems. ',NULL,'2023-10-11',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,NULL,'SAMI Navantia',NULL),('SAP Young Professionals Program Kuwait 2023','United Arab Emirates','Dubai','',' SAP Young Professionals Program Kuwait 2023Education and Training The SAP Young Professionals Program is a free initiative delivered by the Digital Skills Center of SAP . The program, which lasts for 2 months, is designed to give recent graduates the certifications and soft skills required to begin a career as an SAP Associate Consultant. At the end of the training, SAP will work very closely with the program graduates to introduce them to a host of opportunities with SAP customers and partners to work as an SAP Consultant. Work Area Education and Training Location Dubai, AE, 118353',NULL,'2023-10-10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,